<p>Big and bleak, just like László!</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><em>–<a href="https://erikcarter.net/#/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Erik Carter</a></em></p>
<span class="caption"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781250899576" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="246757" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-167-best-book-covers-of-2024/ee6c3163-63eb-4706-9e2e-29562874d6af/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ee6c3163-63eb-4706-9e2e-29562874d6af-scaled.jpg" data-orig-size="1684,2560" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="the wedding people" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;Alison Espach, &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781250899576&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;The Wedding People&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;; cover design and lettering by Nicolette Seeback Ruggiero, art by Fabian Lavater (Henry Holt, July)&lt;/p&gt;
