<p>“It’s giving zine you were never cool enough to have stashed under your bed.”–Emily Temple <strong>←YES</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><em>–<a href="https://www.janet-hansen.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Janet Hansen</a></em></p>
<span class="caption"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780374602635" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="245696" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-167-best-book-covers-of-2024/71hmrbliedl-_sl1500_/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/71HMRBlIEDL._SL1500_.jpg" data-orig-size="937,1500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="sally rooney intermezzo uk" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;Sally Rooney, &lt;em&gt;Intermezzo&lt;/em&gt; (UK edition); cover design and illustration by Kishan Rajani (Faber &#038; Faber, September 24) &lt;/p&gt;
