<p>Matt&#8217;s brain is something else. Beautiful.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><em>–<a href="https://arshraziuddin.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Arsh Raziuddin</a></em></p>
<span class="caption"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780063314870" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="235980" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-11-best-book-covers-of-april-2/91qb5dsycsl-_sl1500_/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/91qB5dsycsL._SL1500_.jpg" data-orig-size="987,1500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Emet North, &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780063314870&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;In&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780063314870&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt; Universes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;; cover design by Robin Bilardello (Harper, April 30)" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;Emet North, &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780063314870&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;In&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780063314870&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt; Universes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;; cover design by Robin Bilardello (Harper, April)&lt;/p&gt;
