<p>Big fan of this arts and crafts project!</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><em>–<a href="https://www.stephenbrayda.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Stephen Brayda</a></em></p>
<span class="caption"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781668028049" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="231348" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/lit-hubs-most-anticipated-books-of-2024/71rupzzgjbl-_sl1500_/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/71ruPzZGjBL._SL1500_.jpg" data-orig-size="994,1500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Rebecca K. Reilly, Greta &#038; Valdin" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;Rebecca K. Reilly, &lt;a href=&quot;https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781668028049&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Greta &amp;amp; Valdin&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;; cover design by Clay Smith (Avid Reader, February)&lt;/p&gt;
